<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0124-zh-4f9ee4fa" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>列子斋口义</title><editor role="translator">Lin Xiyi 林希逸</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>列子斋口义</title>上海：上海师范大学出版社，2016</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0124"><title xml:lang="och">列子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-04-13T00:41:47.503+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0124-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:44:07.374+09:00">「得意」者，造道而有得也。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:44:22+09:00">「進知」者，造道而有知見也。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:44:57.972+09:00">此下却分三轉。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:45:17.252+09:00">「無言」，忘言也，以無言為言，以無知為知。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:46:41.478+09:00">「亦言亦知」者｀請其雖忘言而「無」字猶在也。此是一節。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:50:45.404+09:00">「不」者，是知與言猶在也。「無」者．是「無」字猶在也。「亦」者，未盡之意也。此是一節。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:58:37.405+09:00">此即「從心不踰矩」之說，但說得鼓舞爾。今禪家正用此機關，兼此段文字亦與《傳燈錄》為義處語句同。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T00:55:09.08+09:00">及至淤無所不言，無所不知，而亦無所言，無所知，方為造道之妙。又是一節。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0124_tls_004-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-13T01:04:46.594+09:00">「汝奚妄駭」者，言此乃至人之事，汝何妄以為勞駭？其意蓋謂：汝惟未知至人之事｀所以有此驚駭。我於至人，何可及耶？</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>